revxrsal.commands.process

Interface ValueResolver<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The resolved type

    public interface ValueResolver<T>
    A resolver for resolving values that, by default, require data from the arguments to resolve their value. An example context resolver is finding a player from their name.
